  {
    "path": "about.tagline",
    "source": "<strong>NaiLit</strong> is here to make your nails <em>lit</em> and help you <em>nail it</em>! ✨",
    "translation": "<strong>NaiLit</strong> est là pour rendre vos ongles <em>au top</em> et vous aider à <em>assurer</em> ! ✨",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.intro",
    "source": "We believe that nails should be as <strong>unique as you are</strong>. That is why <strong>NaiLit</strong> offers fully customizable press-on nails designed with you in mind. Using our <em>Nail Dress-Up system</em>, you can choose your shape, length, color, and finish to create a set that is <strong>100% your style</strong>.",
    "translation": "Nous pensons que les ongles devraient être aussi <strong>uniques que vous l'êtes</strong>. C'est pourquoi <strong>NaiLit</strong> propose des press-on nails entièrement personnalisables, conçus pour vous. Grâce à notre <em>Nail Dress-Up system</em>, vous pouvez choisir votre forme, votre longueur, votre couleur et votre finition pour créer un ensemble qui est <strong>100 % votre style</strong>.</translation>",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.craftmanship",
    "source": "Once you have submitted your design, our <strong>expert nail techs</strong> handcraft each set on <em>authentic Gel-X bases</em>. <strong>No 3D printing. No bulky plastic.</strong> Just the perfect balance of thinness, flexibility, and <strong>salon-quality feel</strong> combined with the convenience of press-ons.",
    "translation": "Une fois votre design soumis, nos <strong>prothésistes ongulaires expertes</strong> fabriquent chaque kit à la main sur des <em>bases Gel-X authentiques</em>. <strong>Pas d'impression 3D. Pas de plastique encombrant.</strong> Simplement l'équilibre parfait de finesse, de flexibilité et d'une <strong>sensation de qualité professionnelle</strong>, associé à la praticité des ongles à coller.",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.safety",
    "source": "We are also proud to say that our products are <strong>Trimethylbenzoyl Diphenylphosphine Oxide (TPO)-free</strong> and fully compliant with <strong>EU safety standards</strong>. Beauty should never come at the cost of safety, and <strong>NaiLit</strong> is committed to giving you both.",
    "translation": "Nous sommes également fiers d'affirmer que nos produits sont <strong>sans Trimethylbenzoyl Diphenylphosphine Oxide (TPO)</strong> et entièrement conformes aux <strong>normes de sécurité de l'UE</strong>. La beauté ne devrait jamais se faire au détriment de la sécurité, et <strong>NaiLit</strong> s'engage à vous offrir les deux.",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.kitIncludes",
    "source": "<strong>Every kit comes complete with:</strong>",
    "translation": "<strong>Chaque kit comprend :</strong>",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.adhesiveKit",
    "source": "<strong>1x Nail Adhesive Kit</strong> (featuring both glue and sticker tabs, so you can choose between <em>long-lasting hold</em> or <em>easy reuse</em>)",
    "translation": "<strong>1x Kit d'adhésifs pour ongles</strong> (comprenant à la fois de la colle et des languettes adhésives, afin que vous puissiez choisir entre <em>une tenue longue durée</em> ou <em>une réutilisation facile</em>)",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
    "target_lang": "fr",
    "timestamp": "2025-09-26 23:40:32"
  },
  {
    "path": "about.removalKit",
    "source": "<strong>1x Nail Removal Kit</strong> (so you can change up your look whenever you want, <em>without damage</em>)",
    "translation": "<strong>1x Kit de dépose d'ongles</strong> (pour que vous puissiez changer de look quand vous le souhaitez, <em>sans les abîmer</em>)",
    "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
